{"tid":1426475,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣]佩洛西有一點好多人都忽略左，就係佢否定左香港政府所講既法治","createTime":"2019-08-07T02:28:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T13:57:36.000Z","uid":188176,"like":50,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"31f5493b54ab2114122873f63846a5891570b317","tid":1426475,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:28:30.000Z","msg":"香港政府日日講法治做借口去反對釋放義士<br />\n但香港政府本身就無尊重過法治<br />\n根本法治就唔可以作為香港政府既論點<br />\n而佩洛西發言更加印證左呢個問題<br />\n一個反法治既香港政府日日用「假法治」去欺壓平民<br />\n<br />\nAs they have all summer, today the people of Hong Kong are sending a stirring message to the world: the dreams of freedom, justice and democracy can never be extinguished by injustice and intimidation.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;The extraordinary outpouring of courage from the people of Hong Kong stands in stark contrast to a <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">cowardly government that refuses to respect the rule of law</span></span> or live up to the &lsquo;one country, two systems&rsquo; framework which was guaranteed more than two decades ago.  The people of Hong Kong deserve the true autonomy that was promised, with the full rights guaranteed by the Hong Kong Basic Law and international agreements.  The Legislative Council must finally take long-overdue measures to meet the legitimate democratic aspirations of the Hong Kong people &ndash; starting with completely and immediately withdrawing the widely-repudiated extradition bill.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Democrats and Republicans in Congress stand united with the people of Hong Kong in demanding the hopeful, free and democratic future that is their right.  We reiterate the call of the Tom Lantos Human Rights Commission Co-Chairs Congressman Jim McGovern and Congressman Chris Smith to the Trump Administration to suspend future sales of munitions and crowd control equipment to the Hong Kong police force.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;When we return to Washington, the bipartisan, bicameral Congress will begin our work to advance the Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act, and fight to preserve democratic freedoms and the rule of law in Hong Kong.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"8c191d926397677da57123a3dd5fc07f9dc92d43","tid":1426475,"uid":188176,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:31:53.000Z","msg":"以佩洛西發言做基礎<br />\n去反擊香港政府既假法治"},{"pid":"78f1668bdbc925d5b0a3e85a41a7a27f58e44b66","tid":1426475,"uid":193233,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:34:01.000Z","msg":"根本就係人治<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bccfc75cb499c45e7af25c637b1f8464d2597f29","tid":1426475,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:34:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfbef2f7669f6793237f0ea3c358ea65f00c6066","tid":1426475,"uid":188176,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"78f1668bdbc925d5b0a3e85a41a7a27f58e44b66","tid":1426475,"uid":193233,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:34:01.000Z","msg":"根本就係人治<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:40:33.000Z","msg":"其實成個政府都係用法治去反擊<br />\n因為法治，我要拉晒d義士<br />\n因為法治，警察可以依法打柒平民<br />\n因為法治，元朗恐怖襲擊同律政司慢慢傾，等多d人好似福建會夠膽發動多d恐襲<br />\n因為法治，警察可以亂放催淚彈<br />\n因為法治，可以亂告暴動<br />\n因為法治，可以亂拘留任何人48小時<br />\n<br />\n香港政府既「假法治」係佢既命根黎"},{"pid":"3c6d5c3a1ab0ef122935ea34075bc1a84600857a","tid":1426475,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:40:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"feb9f6df0fe01da11a842c7f70af263db64b8d5c","tid":1426475,"uid":267838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:44:53.000Z","msg":"人治+軍政府"},{"pid":"8dab923b14607727652d8698a8549dfa90a319ff","tid":1426475,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:48:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.